##############################
1 - Coding convention

1.1 Ten ham:
- Chu dau tien viet thuong, cac ki tu cua keyword duoc viet hoa
- Bat dau tu dong tu
1.2 Ten bien:
- Chu dau tien viet thuong va cac ki tu cua keyword duoc viet hoa
- Bat dau tu danh tu

2 - Cau truc he thong:

2.1 Thuc hien theo mo hinh MVC
- Model
- View
- Controller

2.2 Theo kien truc 3 layers 3 tiers
- Se duoc tich hop them DTO
- Dien giai nhu sau:
 + Model: (DAO) se tuong tac voi DB o tang thap nhat
 + >>>>>>DTO se tuong tac tu DAO va tang tren controller, xu ly luon logic business
 + Controller: xu ly data va tra ve cho view, tuong tac voi DTO ma thoi
 + View: xu ly show data len UI va tuong tac voi controller

2.3 Xu ly da ngon ngu: config/locales

2.4 Xu ly constant:
- message
- error code, object type
